{"tid":2371705,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"1861年1月19日，英方接收九龍及昂船州","createTime":"2021-01-19T05:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T05:24:36.000Z","uid":289214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"edfa3380ccadcace512402d30794c59ecdadf21e","tid":2371705,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"blue\"><strong>160年前</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式的移交儀式於1861年1月19日舉行。當日2000多名英軍官兵渡海前往尖沙咀參加儀式。下午3時，額爾金在巴夏禮、港督總督羅便臣和正臬司（即首席大法官）亞當斯（William Adams）的陪同下抵達會場。清廷出席的有新安縣令、大鵬協副將、九龍司巡檢和九龍城一名較低級軍官共4人。在額爾金同清朝官員簡短交談後（由巴夏禮翻譯），巴夏禮把一個裝滿泥土的紙袋塞給清朝代表，讓後者再把紙袋交給他，象徵領土移交。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wetoasthk.com/%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D/?utm_source=facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR0BO8IkJdICoaHifDGuRJ6AEew5kTtbFsDZTnPLSXhEnR55gMZVhR-oQ50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wetoasthk.com%2F%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2594%25B6%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR0BO8IkJdICoaHifDGuRJ6AEew5kTtbFsDZTnPLSXhEnR55gMZVhR-oQ50&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrIyfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=da61626e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wetoasthk.com/%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D/?utm_source=facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR0BO8IkJdICoaHifDGuRJ6AEew5kTtbFsDZTnPLSXhEnR55gMZVhR-oQ50</a>"}]}